      "raw_text": "Industrial Workers of the World,\nunder whose auspices Elizabeth\nGurley Flynn will speak at the Tur-\nner hall tonight on Law and Or\nder\" have extended an especial in\nvitation 10 Mayor \\. S. Pratt and\nto other city and county officials\nto attend the meeting. The woman\nrevolutionist has Just returned\nfrom a lecture tour in behalf Of\nfree speech in Canada."
